**Stalker** | Townsfolk Power
__Basics__
Each day, the Stalker may assign two extra votes to a player in the current day’s polls.
__Details__
Each day, the Stalker may threaten a player. That player will have 2 more invisible votes against them on the daily polls. These additional votes not revealed, instead the threated player may win the lynch even if they dont have the most votes. The threatened player is not informed that they are threatened.

__Simplified__
Each day, the Stalker may assign two extra invisible votes to a player in the current day’s polls.
